mixin Guide()
    section.cricketsquad__guide.container
        h2.move-zoom How to Play & Dominate Fantasy Cricket

        p.move-left Ready to turn your cricket passion into an epic gaming experience? CricketSquad lets you build your dream team, compete with others, and climb the leaderboard with smart strategies. Whether you're a rookie or a seasoned player, our step-by-step guide will have you scoring big in no time. Let’s dive in and master the game!

        div.move-right
            span 📱
            h3 Getting Started with Fantasy Cricket
            p Jump into the action by downloading the CricketSquad app. Pick your squad from real-life players and craft the perfect lineup. Your team’s success depends on your strategic picks—so choose wisely! Track real-time match stats and earn points as your players perform on the field.

        div.move-left
            span 🎯
            h3 Sign Up & Log In
            p Kick off your CricketSquad journey in seconds! Simply download the app, sign up using your email or social media, and verify your details. Once you’re in, explore contests, join challenges, and start playing instantly!

        div.move-right
            span ✉️
            h3 Build Your Ultimate Team
            p Select top players based on their recent form and upcoming matches. Need to tweak your squad? No problem! Adjust your lineup before the match starts and outplay your competition with sharp decision-making. 

        div.move-left
            span 🏆
            h3 Score Big & Climb the Leaderboard
            p Every run, wicket, and boundary earns you points! Keep an eye on live match updates and track your team’s performance in real time. Make smart substitutions and dominate the leaderboard to prove you're the ultimate fantasy cricket strategist!

            p Fantasy cricket isn’t just a game—it’s your chance to rule the pitch!


        +Link({
            class: 'btn cricketsquad__btn',
            href: 'contact.html',
            text: 'Download Now',
        })
